subject: Tennis
United States Open (Tennis)
lead_paragraph: In front of an overflow crowd at the Grandstand, Donald Young absorbed the electricity from the fans and overcame a two-set deficit to beat Viktor Troicki, 4-6, 0-6, 7-6 (3), 6-2, 6-4.
